# Blender 5.1+ API

## Do not use

```python
# ❌ Dict-like IDProperty on data-blocks
obj["my_key"] = value
modifier["Input_2"] = 2

# ❌ Deprecated / fragile color access when proxy returns empty .data
mesh.color_attributes.active_color.data  # verify; prefer attributes API
```

## Do use

```python
# Custom object data — register RNA in addon properties module
from ..addon_properties import store_custom_metadata

# Geometry Nodes sockets — helper module, not dict access
from .geonodes_modifier_helpers import get_nodes_modifier_input, set_nodes_modifier_inputs
from .addon_constants import SUBDIV_SOCKET_CREASE

# Mesh attributes (face sets, color, etc.)
mesh.attributes[attr_name].data.foreach_get("value", arr)
```

## Version bumps

On Blender update breakage, check [Python API release notes](https://developer.blender.org/docs/release_notes/) for your target version before adding compatibility shims. See also `blender-addon-global-api-compat.mdc`.
